  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/e41c329e18e68b0ac672e3f802bedb6b.poster.avif?t=1763980260\" width=700 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/e41c329e18e68b0ac672e3f802bedb6b.webm?t=1763980260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/e41c329e18e68b0ac672e3f802bedb6b.mp4?t=1763980260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Cause mayhem like its the year 2000 again with fast paced gameplay and tons of weapons at your disposal!<br>Take on challenges and try get all the platinum trophies, learn the layout of every level and difficulty and try to beat your time!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/e6b533eb4bc8b7cfa1c41f06819a51af.poster.avif?t=1763980260\" width=700 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/e6b533eb4bc8b7cfa1c41f06819a51af.webm?t=1763980260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/e6b533eb4bc8b7cfa1c41f06819a51af.mp4?t=1763980260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Challenges can consist of pig racing, flying an apache, playing chicken with train, being a firefighter, pint smashing and much more!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/b2ac07ebbc16b1458bba5a961a9ca331.poster.avif?t=1763980260\" width=700 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/b2ac07ebbc16b1458bba5a961a9ca331.webm?t=1763980260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/b2ac07ebbc16b1458bba5a961a9ca331.mp4?t=1763980260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Environments have lots of detail to interactive with like smashing windows, potting ball on a pool table, smashing plates, blowing up crates or even using the items in the environment like a fire extinguisher!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/1299328cb05111a848b4d90a111ca824.poster.avif?t=1763980260\" width=700 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/1299328cb05111a848b4d90a111ca824.webm?t=1763980260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533470/extras/1299328cb05111a848b4d90a111ca824.mp4?t=1763980260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Create your perfect map using the mapmaker!<br>Place tiles, create multiplayer maps, create story missions, add triggers, edit how AI function and even change the look of your map.<br>Share your maps using the Steam Workshop!<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 9 STORY MISSIONS.<br></li><li> 30+ CRAZY CHALLENGE MISSIONS.<br></li><li> INTERACT WITH YOUR ENVIRONMENT.<br></li><li> PLAY ONLINE AGAINST OTHERS IN MODES LIKE DEATHMATCH, CAPTURE THE BAG, VIRUS AND MANY MORE!.<br></li><li> *USE THE MAPMAKER TO CREATE YOUR OWN MAPS!</li></ul><br>*MAPMAKER IS A VERY EARLY FEATURE AND WILL BE UPDATED IN THE COMING WEEKS WITH MORE TILES.",
